      <content type="html" xml:base="https://www.bnlawrence.net//science/2023/06/infrastructure-strategy/">&lt;p&gt;One of the many reasons I have been so quiet of late is that I have been bevering away on a new ENES&lt;sup id=&quot;fnref:1&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#fn:1&quot; class=&quot;footnote&quot;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; infrastructure strategy for climate modelling. We now have a draft out for public feedback, so please do comment!&lt;/p&gt;

