    &lt;li id=&quot;fn:1&quot;&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;ENES is the European Network for Earth System modelling - main website is at &lt;a href=&quot;https://portal.enes.org&quot;&gt;https://portal.enes.org&lt;/a&gt;. (Footnote added, 21/06/23). &lt;a href=&quot;#fnref:1&quot; class=&quot;reversefootnote&quot;&gt;&amp;#8617;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
